    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_1_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_1",
      "description": "Hey there! I\u2019m parting ways with my absolute pride and joy, and honestly, it\u2019s a total dream. This car is in truly incredible shape\u2014it\u2019s been tucked away in a garage and treated like royalty, so it still has that 'new car' feel inside and out! It drives like a charm and looks absolutely stunning. I\u2019ve loved every mile in it, and I know the next owner will too. Come take a look and see for yourself!",
      "price": 44500.0,
