    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_5_listing_5",
      "firm_id": "sybil_5",
      "description": "We are pleased to present this exemplary vehicle, maintained in impeccable showroom condition. This specimen represents the zenith of automotive preservation, featuring a flawless exterior finish and an interior that remains in pristine, original state. Every component has been meticulously curated to ensure mechanical absolute perfection and aesthetic integrity. This is an invitation to the discerning driver to acquire a vehicle that transcends the standard pre-owned experience. Professional inspections are welcomed to verify its superlative status.",
