      "description": "Hey there! You've seriously got to see this beauty in person. It\u2019s honestly like it just rolled off the showroom floor\u2014absolutely spotless inside and out! I've babied this car since day one, and it still drives like a total dream. If you're looking for that 'new car' feeling without the massive dealership price tag, this is the one for you! Come take it for a spin, I promise you're going to fall in love! \u2728",
