    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_7_listing_7",
      "firm_id": "sybil_7",
      "description": "Offered is an investment-grade 2004 BMW M3 (E46) featuring the high-revving S54 3.2L inline-six engine and a desirable Getrag 6-speed manual gearbox. This example is mechanically superlative, boasting a fully overhauled dual-VANOS system and preventative rod bearing replacement to ensure the longevity of the 8,000 RPM redline. The rear subframe has been professionally reinforced with plates, addressing the chassis's primary structural vulnerability. Power is delivered through a factory M-Variable limited-slip differential, providing precise torque vectoring. Every bushing is tight, the throttle response from the individual throttle bodies is instantaneous, and the compression across all six cylinders is within factory specifications. This is a turn-key masterpiece for the purist seeking peak analog performance.",
